Make your default GitHub repository visibility private

Default visibility of new GitHub repository is public in GitHub which is not Enterprise version. However, you might want to make new GitHub repository as private by default. That is why this extension exists. This extension change default repository visibility to private. This extension may make you feel comfortable to make new repository if you often make private repositories.
